Consider the following class and code segment:

```java
public class Lamp {
    private static int onCount = 0;
    private boolean isOn;

    public Lamp() { isOn = false; }

    public void turnOn() {
        if (!isOn) {
            isOn = true;
            onCount++;
        }
    }

    public void turnOff() {
        if (isOn) { isOn = false; }
    }

    public static int getOnCount() { return onCount; }
}
```

```java
Lamp x = new Lamp();
Lamp y = new Lamp();
x.turnOn();
x.turnOn();
y.turnOn();
x.turnOff();
y.turnOn();
System.out.println(Lamp.getOnCount());
```

What is the output?

